# MkDoxy

**[MkDoxy](https://mkdoxy.kubaandrysek.cz/)** plugin for **[MkDocs](https://www.mkdocs.org/)** generates API documentation based on **[Doxygen](https://www.doxygen.nl)** comments and **[code snippets](/intro)** in your markdown files.

